Show HN: Script to prevent same day meetings on my corporate calendar
text:
Hi,

I have a corporate job, I have most of my notifications off, and try to work in blocks of focus time.

When colleagues schedule same day meetings I often miss it because I saw it too late. Which makes me feel guilty.

This tool helped me avoid feeling guilty by preventing last-minute meetings.
